#. [message]: id=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:319
#, fuzzy
msgid "Orcs are pressing on us from all directions! To arms!"
msgstr ""
"Guarda, ci sono tantissimi orchi che arrivano da tutte le parti! Alle armi!"

#. [message]: id=Velon
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:323
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Hold, Kalenz. The Ka'lian council should discuss our response. Maybe we can "
"reach an agreement with them!"
msgstr ""
"Fermo Kalenz. Il consiglio dovrebbe discutere di questo argomento. Forse "
"possiamo giungere a un accordo con loro!"

#. [message]: id=Qumseh
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:327
#, fuzzy
msgid "Surrender or die, tree-shaggers!"
msgstr "Arrendetevi o morirete, luridi elfi!"

#. [message]: id=Velon
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:331
#, fuzzy
msgid "They are too many. We have no choice but to submit!"
msgstr "Sono troppi. Temo che non abbiamo altra scelta che arrenderci!"

#. [message]: id=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:335
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Elves must never surrender to these foul beasts! Who will fight them beside "
"me?"
msgstr ""
"Gli elfi non si arrenderanno mai di fronte a queste belve malvagie! Chi è "
"con me?"

#. [message]: id=Landar
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:339
#, fuzzy
msgid "We will follow you, Kalenz - but where can we go? We are surrounded!"
msgstr "Ti seguiremo - ma dove vuoi andare? Siamo circondati!"

#. [message]: id=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:343
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We must reach the elvish council in Ka'lian and enlist their help to "
"recapture our home. Let's storm the orcs' southern outpost before more "
"enemies arrive!"
msgstr ""
"Dobbiamo raggiungere il consiglio degli elfi a Kali'an e chiedere il loro "
"aiuto per riprendere la nostra patria. Dobbiamo andare a sud ovest per "
"riunirci con i nostri fratelli. Martelliamo il loro avamposto a sud prima "
"che ne arrivino altri!"

#. [message]: id=Anduilas
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:347
#, fuzzy
msgid "Very well, Kalenz - lead us!"
msgstr "Bene Kalenz, guidaci!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:363
#, fuzzy
msgid "You trifled with the wrong elf!"
msgstr "Ti sei messo contro l'elfo sbagliato!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:374
msgid "Take that, you orcish scum!"
msgstr "Prendi questo, feccia d'orco!"

#. [message]: id=Velon
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:388
msgid "We surrender!"
msgstr "Ci arrendiamo!"

#. [message]: id=Graur-Tan
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:392
msgid "Did I mention that we take no prisoners? Die!"
msgstr "Non ti avevo ancora detto che non facciamo prigionieri? Muori!"

#. [message]: id=Velon
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:396
msgid ""
"Kalenz was right and I was wrong. Go; join Kalenz while yet you can. I and "
"the remaining elders will cover your retreat as best we may."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: id=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:415
#, fuzzy
msgid "We have escaped them, but we will not forget. We shall return!"
msgstr "Adesso dobbiamo andarcene, ma non dimenticheremo. Noi ritorneremo!"

#. [message]: id=Graur-Tan
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:419
msgid "You won't get very far! After them!"
msgstr "Non andrete lontano! Inseguiamoli!"

#. [message]: id=Velon
#: data/campaigns/Legend_of_Wesmere/scenarios/01_The_Uprooting.cfg:450
msgid "Flee, Kalenz...our hopes ride with you..."
msgstr ""

